beer.beer_description:
The teams at Beer Jerk and Carwyn Cellars brought together 12 Aussie and 12 Kiwi breweries to create 12 brand new, exciting and innovative beers, brewed and released simultaneously in both Australia and New Zealand.

We were paired with Alibi Brewing Co located on Waiheke Island (to the west of Auckland).

Mike and Bernard put their heads together to create the recipe for a style of beer neither has made before (we then messed up and accidentally put in Idaho-7 instead of Simcoe…but accidents happens). Trust them to try a completely new style of beer to brew as their first collab...
